ChurchMetrics,is,a,web,based,church,management,service,that,helps,churches,keep,track,of,important,information,Trackable,information,includes,attendance,donations,baptisms,and,more,Historical,data,can,be,reviewed,in,the,form,of,charts,and,reports,This,data,can,be,accessed,from,any,computer,with,internet,access,or,via,an,iOS,or,Android,application,Data,is,also,programmatically,accessible,via,REST,API